name: LocalEvents

”Alexa open local events”

skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: local events
des:
This objective of this Alexa Skill is two-folds: 1) to provide a skill for users to obtain local events nearby on a timeframe: today, tomorrow, weekend 2) to provide a skill for users to obtain local discounts/specials on a timeframe: today, tomorrow, weekend.

Version 1.0 only achieve the first objective
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
